item.description:
Timetable Chat Bot This was the world&rsquo;s first chat bot for helping students with their timetables.
Written in Node.js and using NLP and ML, students could ask free form questions and receive an immediate response, for example:
  Student: &ldquo;When is the next lecture for MATH101?&rdquo;
Bot: &ldquo;There is a lecture for MATH101 on Tuesday at 9.00am in Roscoe Theatre A.&quot;
Student: &ldquo;How do I find Roscoe Theatre A?&rdquo;
